Class QuantityCollection

java.lang.Object
au.csiro.pathling.fhirpath.collection.Collection
au.csiro.pathling.fhirpath.collection.QuantityCollection
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable, Equatable, Numeric, StringCoercible
public class QuantityCollection extends Collection implements Comparable, StringCoercible, Numeric
Represents a FHIRPath expression which refers to an element of type Quantity.
Author:
John Grimes
